{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf\">Asdf</a> est un gestionnaire de version (version manager) pour Python, Node.js, Ruby, etc. Il permet de changer de version pour chaque langage de programmation sans se prendre la tête.</p><h2>Installation</h2><p>Si vous êtes sur Arch Linux :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">yay -S --noconfirm asdf-vm\n</code></pre></div><p>Puis ajoutez les 2 lignes suivantes dans votre fichier <code>~/.bashrc</code> ou <code>~/.zshrc</code>.</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">export ASDF_DATA_DIR=$HOME/.asdf\nexport PATH=$PATH:$ASDF_DATA_DIR/shims\n</code></pre></div><h2>Utilisation</h2><p>Pour installer un plugin (Node.js, Python, Ruby, etc...), utilisez la commande suivante :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf plugin add nodejs\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour lister toutes les versions de Node.js :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf list all nodejs\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour installer une version spécifique de Node.js :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf install nodejs 22.19.0\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour définir une version globale par défaut :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf set -u nodejs 22.19.0\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour définir une version locale :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf set nodejs 22.19.0\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour connaitre la version en cours :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf current\n</code></pre></div><p>Revenir à la version système d&#x27;origine :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf set -u nodejs system\n</code></pre></div><p>Lorsque vous installer un package npm global (ex : <code>npm i -g yarn</code>), n&#x27;oubliez pas d&#x27;exécuter la commande suivante pour pouvoir accéder au package :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">asdf reshim nodejs\n</code></pre></div><blockquote class=\"callout note\">\n                    \n                        <div class=\"callout-title\">\n                            <div class=\"callout-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"6\"></line><path d=\"M7.5 20.5 19 9l-4-4L3.5 16.5 2 22z\"></path></svg></div>\n                            <div class=\"callout-title-inner\">note</div>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"callout-content\">\n                        <p>Avec Python, si vous rencontrez une erreur lors du lancement d&#x27;une commande pip install, exécutez là de cette manière : sudo -E pip install --break-system-packages <package>.</package></p>\n                    </div>\n                </blockquote><hr/><p>Références :</p><ul>\n<li>https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf</li>\n</ul></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Asdf.md","fileName":"Asdf","title":"Asdf","comments":true,"permalink":"asdf","datePublished":"2022-06-16T11:53","dateUpdated":"2025-03-08T09:28:00","publish":true,"rss":true},"__N_SSG":true}